                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for John Hammond &amp;lt;john.hammond@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/0ddbe7a0-0314-11e4-b192-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/0ddbe7a0-0314-11e4-b192-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_2 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test_2 returned 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: insanity 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MDT0000 is running OOM in insanity test_1 or before.&lt;/p&gt;

